Subject: Web Portal Not Working
Description: We migrated the SQL database for StealthAudit following the instructions on the website, this as worked fine and the console on the server is working correctly along with all monitoring, however when trying to login to the web portal we now get the following messaging for all accounts "Unable to contact the SQL Server Database". The new SQL database is SQL 2022.
Solution_Comment__c: Old database server was configured in AIC, change to the new one after the migration
